    "rationale": "Although the underlying COU assessment concluded Not Accepted due to MRL 5 credibility gaps, this UnitOfAssurance package is formally accepted as a complete and traceable record of the credibility evidence state. The package documents all 13 ASME V&V 40 factors, captures the epistemic gaps transparently, and satisfies the evidentiary requirements for regulatory submission as a gap-disclosure artifact. Acceptance of the package does not constitute acceptance of the model for clinical use.",
